                  發問者的評分
                













 其實看起來符號學和語言學、人類學、建築學和設計都有很深的關聯 
都是譯碼（encode）與解碼（decode）的關係。 

符號學是一種「關於符徵(signs)與意義顯化(signification)的科學」，而社會符號學則是用符號學原理來解讀各種社會符徵以及探究社會意義的學問－至於它之是否屬於一門科學，則已經不是最重要的問題。 

相關書籍 ：    
李幼蒸(1993)《理論符號學導論》。北京：中國社會科學出版社。  
Barthes, R. (1991)（李幼蒸 譯）《寫作的零度：結構主義文學理論文選》(Writing Degree Zero )。臺北﹕時報文化出版社。  
Barthes, R. (1964/1967) Elements of Semiology. New York: Hill & Wang.  
Barthes, R. (1972) Mythologies. New York: Noonday Press.  
Barthes, R. (1993)（孫乃修 譯）《符號禪意東洋風》(L'empire des signes )。臺北﹕台灣商務印書館。  
Barthes, R. (1995)（許綺玲 譯）《明室：攝影扎記》(La chambre claire )臺北﹕時報文化出版社。  
Baudrillard, J. ( Ed. by Poster, M.) (1988) Jean Baudrillard: Selected Writings. Oxford: Polity Press.  
Blonsky, M. (Ed.) (1985) On Signs: A Semiotics Reader. Oxford: Blackwell.  
Boon, J. A. (1979) "Saussure/ Peirce a propos Language, Society and Culture." In  I.P. Winner & J. Umiker-Sebeok (eds.) Semiotics of Culture. New York: Mouton.    
Eco, U. (1976) A Theory of Semiotics.  Bloomington, Indiana: Indiana University Press.  
Fiske, J.（張錦華等譯）(1995)《傳播符號學理論》(Introduction to Communication Studies)。臺北：遠流。  
Gottdiener, M.  & Lagopoulos, A. Ph. (Eds.)(1986) The City and the Sign: An Introduction to Urban Semiotics.  New York : Columbia University Press.  
Gottdiener, M. (1995) Postmodern Semiotics: Material Culture and the Forms of Postmodern Life. Oxford: Blackwell.  
Greimas, A. J. (1991) The Social Sciences: A Semiotic View.  Minneapolis: University of Minnesota Press.  
Halliday, M.A.K. (1978) Language as Social Semiotic: The Social Interpretation of Language and Meaning. London: Edward Arnold.  
Hawkes, T. （陳永寬 譯）(1988)《結構主義與符號學》(Structuralism and Semiotics )。臺北﹕南方。  
Hodge, R & Kress, G. (1988) Social Semiotics.  Ithaca: Cornell University Press.  
Manning, P.K. (1987) Semiotics and Fieldworks. London: Sage.  
Mertz, E. & Parmentier, R. J. (Eds.)(1985) Semiotic Mediation: Sociocultural and Psychological Perspectives. New York: Academic Press.  
Sebeok, T. A. (1994) An Introduction to Semiotics. London: Pinter.   
Thibault, P. J. (1991) Social Semiotics as Praxis: Text, Social Meaning Making, and Nabokov's Ada. Minneapolis: University of Minnesota Press.  
Winner, T. G. (1979) "Some Fundamental Concepts Leading to a Semiotics of Culture." In I.P. Winner & J. Umiker-Sebeok (eds.) Semiotics of Culture. New York: Mouton.





